      <p>
        Before joining Verisk Health's Payment Integrity Division, Karthik most recently served as Vice President of Analytics at ISO Innovative Analytics (iiA) where he oversaw all analytical development activities across P&C, Healthcare, and Mortgage verticals. Prior to joining iiA, Karthik led the Analytical Services organization at Fireman's Fund Insurance Company (a company of Allianz), where his team had notable successes in deploying analytics in claim fraud detection, underwriting rules optimization, customer segmentation, and many other claims and operational initiatives. Karthik has a Ph.D. in Machine Learning from Iowa State University and over 20 research publications in diverse areas such as neural networks, evolutionary algorithms, spatial learning and neuro-cognitive modeling and is the co-editor of an MIT Press book on Evolutionary Synthesis of Intelligent Agents.
